body:
I'm fully dedicated to updating this mod, even if it might be scuffed, but I'm 
trying my best to improve it and make it look better and more presentable, while also hopefully keeping up with a weekly update schedule, unless school or vacations interfere;

This mod is divided by chapters and seasons, depending on the version number: 1.y.z is season update, x.1.z is chapter update, and x.y.1 is a fix/in chapter update;

Enough yapping, THIS MOD IS DEDICATED TO ADDING ANOMALIES TO YOUR WORLD! THAT'S RIGHT, WEIRD SILLY STUFF FOR YOU TO EXPLORE, and to top that off.. _**FANCY**_ weapons for you to make! with passives and special abilities, with, of course, maintaining balance.
